   DIS 2024 COMPANION},
Year = {2024},
Pages = {275-278},
Note = {2024 Designing Interactive Systems Conference, Copenhagen, DENMARK, JUL
   01-05, 2024},
Abstract = {This project explores how generative AI can assist electronic music
   producers in composing rhythms and melodies. Based on detailed user
   research with electronic music producers, a central tension in music
   composition is between authorial control and unpredictability. This
   paper presents Ideary, a concept where users explore the latent space of
   their custom generative AI models through an XY pad based on extensive
   user research. A user evaluation shows that music producers responded
   positively to this approach.},
