Year = {2023},
Volume = {11},
Number = {2},
Month = {APR},
Abstract = {With the continuous developments of information technology, advanced
   computer technology and information technology have been promoted and
   used in the field of music. As one of the products of the rapid
   development of information technology, Artificial Intelligence (AI)
   involves many interdisciplinary subjects, adding new elements to music
   education. By analyzing the advantages of AI in music education, this
   paper systematically summarizes the application of AI in music education
   and discusses the development prospects of AI in music education. With
   the aid of AI, the combination of intelligent technology and on-site
   teaching solves the lack of individuation in the traditional mode and
   enhances students' interest in learning.},
