Abstract = {Music is an indispensable part of people's lives. It can make people
   relaxed and can become a way for people to socialize. However, it is a
   big challenge for ordinary people to generate music, because they do not
   have professional music knowledge. Deep learning can solve this. By
   using the LSTM model, we can convert music into music scores and express
   them with specific numbers. Then pass the data packet into the model,
   and the model will guess the next music based on the existing music
